rep david obey dwis foreign aid subcommittee chairman 
called bushs request for 5 billion in military aid an increase 
of 300 million over the current level particularly quaint 
given the changes in the world instead the panel approved just 
over 46 billion in military aid to friends and allies around the 
globe 
