their lifestyle a community grieving for the carefree days forever 
lost 
it isnt enough to say dont because no adult can live with 
dont for a whole lifetime especially when it comes to sex 
reinfeld said 
the american foundation for aids research has awarded 145000 
to communitybased aids groups to create a national relapse 
prevention network advertising campaigns in san francisco 
addressing relapse and a series of seminars in los angeles based on 
the gmhcs keep it up relapse workshops 
