west germany gave final approval today 
to the economic merger with east germany a move that will 
effectively unite the two countries after 40 years of cold war 
division 
parliaments upper house or bundesrat passed the state treaty 
a day after the east german parliament and the powerful lower house 
of the west german parliament approved it 
with the decision the mighty west german mark becomes the 
official currency in east germany on july 2 the historic pact 
marks the de facto unification of germany and the end of 40 years 
of communism in east germany 
