socalled peace dividend you will get neither gen colin 
powell chairman of the joint chiefs of staff said in a speech to 
the national press club 
as we get smaller we also need to get better if we do it too 
fast we dont get better we get hollow he said warning 
against a return to the postvietnam war and world war ii 
reductions 
powells blunt remarks were his first major commentary on the 
