unitarianuniversalists have always affirmed that religion is 
not a sunday morning experience schultz said in an interview 
unitarianuniversalists believe religious principles need to be 
brought to bear on public policy questions and the political events 
of the day 
about 3000 delegates were expected to attend the conference of 
the bostonbased church which claims about 190000 members and 
