james johnston to prove he was ineffective counsel in the 1985 
firstdegree murder trial here he was quizzed closely about why he 
did not introduce possible mitigating circumstances to convince the 
jury to sentence his client to life in prison instead of the 
electric chair 
ms buenoano was sentenced to death for the fatal arsenic 
